activity and stability</A> (L. Linders) </LI>
<LI><A HREF="suzanne.html">The implementation of quantitative risk analysis
in HACCP for the production of safe foods</A> (S. van Gerwen) </LI>
<LI><A HREF="wijtzes.html">Modelling the microbial quality of foods</A>
(T. Wijtzes) </LI>
<LI><A HREF="erwin.html">Valorization of brewery spent grains</A> (E. Kuiper)
</LI>
<LI><A HREF="floor.html">Reactor design for the enzymatic synthesis of
oligosaccharides</A> (F. Boon) </LI>
<LI><A HREF="dirk.html">Modelling microbial interactions</A> (D. Martens)
</LI>
</UL>

