<P>
<HR>The file <I><A HREF="search.zip">search.zip (version 22/04/96)</A></I>
contains an index file of all words in the PhD-project pages of the OSPT
and an executable file (for DOS based machines) to search for a certain
keyword. The executable file creates a world wide web document (result.htm)
containing hyperlinks to all pages containing the supplied keyword.<BR>
A <I>readme.txt</I> file is also included.</P>

