<BODY BACKGROUND="../../back/tile2.gif">

<H3>Phase C:  group design of processes and apparatus<HR></H3>

An industrial design project will be carried out during this phase in a small team (max. 8 students). The team will be advised by an experienced designer from the industry. The total time for the project is 600 hours.<P>

<HR>

<A HREF="index.html"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="../../pic/home.gif"></A> Process &amp; Apparatus Development School Delft

