<BODY BACKGROUND="../../back/tile2.gif">

<H3>Phase D: individual designproject<HR></H3>

This phase, which will be carried out mainly during the second year of the course,  consists of an individual project conformed to a design, supported by (experimental) development work, followed by the writing a report and a presentation of the results. this phase takes 1680 hours of which at least 40% will be needed for the design component.<P>

<HR>

<A HREF="index.html"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="../../pic/home.gif"></A> Process &amp; Apparatus Development School Delft

