<BODY BACKGROUND="../../back/tile2.gif">

<H3>Individual year assignment Process Development Course<HR></H3>

During the second year the members of the course participate, to the accompaniment of teachers of the course, in a process development project. This project will be done fully individual.<P>

The projects are part of the program "Methodic Process Development" and are contract research which is always in close co-operation with the industry. Sometimes the entire project, or a part of it, is done in the industry.<P>

