<CENTER><H2>Process Systems Engineering</H2></CENTER>

<B>RESEARCH THEME</B><P>

<UL>
<LI>Measuring, modelling and controlling interacting phenomena of complex process systems from micro- to macro-level.<BR>
<LI>Focal area: Polymers.<P>
</UL>

This unifies the Process Analysis and the Process Integration &amp; Dynamics activities.<P>

<B>TOPICS</B><P>

<UL>
<B>Process Analysis and Chemometrics</B>
<LI>Plant-wide Process Analysis
<LI>Chemometrics
</UL>

<UL>
<B>Process Dynamics &amp; Integration</B>
<LI>Polymer Systems
<LI>Process Integration with Dynamics &amp; Control
<LI>Artificial Intelligence Supported Process Synthesis
<LI>Transport Phenomena
</UL>

