<DOCNO>WT25-B29-207</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA011-000116-B042-8</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://utct.ct.utwente.nl:80/~ospt/minipost95/tud/emile_an.html 130.89.50.60 19970216192024 text/html 3589
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sunday, 16-Feb-97 19:13:50 GMT
Server: NCSA/1.3
