<DOCNO>WT25-B29-371</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA011-000119-B031-329</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://utct.ct.utwente.nl:80/~ospt/minipost95/luw/pieter.html 130.89.50.60 19970216195427 text/html 2810
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sunday, 16-Feb-97 19:47:52 GMT
