<A NAME="institutional-partners"></A><DT><STRONG>Institutional Partners</STRONG></DT>
<DD><IMG SRC="../media/gifs/diabull.gif" WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10 HSPACE="5"><A HREF="partners/partners.html">Partnership for Distributed Learning</A>
</DL>
</TD>

<TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT>
<IMG SRC="../media/gifs/1X17pix.gif" ALIGN=LEFT WIDTH="17" HEIGHT="435">

<P>Several IAT initiatives focus on assisting educational and corporate institutions to make effective, efficient use of technology in education and training.  The IAT Corporate Partners Program gives companies the opportunity to understand the needs of the educational community and produce products and services that fulfill those needs.  The Partnership for Distributed Learning assists other educational institutions in the development of technology solutions to common problems.  In addition to its own consortia, the IAT participates in EDUCOM's National Learning Infrastructure Initiative.  Find out more information about our institutional activities by following the links at left.
</TABLE>
