</DL>
</TD>

<TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT  WIDTH="440">
<IMG SRC="../media/gifs/1X17pix.gif" ALIGN=LEFT WIDTH="17" HEIGHT="430">

<P>The IAT sees information technology as a means, not an end. With that in mind, we concentrate on developing and distributing tools that make the transference of knowledge from teacher to student more efficient and rewarding. Examples include software tools such as Nouvelles Dimensions - a multimedia CD-ROM product for teaching French listening comprehension, Toolkit for Interactive Mathematics - an award-winning secondary school mathematics program, and WebApp - a software program that dramatically simplifies installation and execution of software via the World Wide Web; as well as periodic satellite broadcasts and technical papers covering the latest trends in information and instructional technology. Find out more about these and other IAT technology activities by clicking on a link at left.

</TABLE>
</TABLE>
