         <LI><A HREF="http://www.ozemail.com.au/~caveman/Stravinsky/">Igor Stravinsky</A><P>

        <LI><A HREF="http://www.utu.fi/%7Ehansalmi/wagner.spml">Richard Wagner Archive</>
