<CENTER><FONT SIZE=+2><STRONG>Distance Learning Resources</STRONG></FONT>
<P>
Compiled by: Carolyn Kotlas, MSLS<BR>
Institute for Academic Technology<BR>
Last revised: January 17, 1997
</CENTER>
<P>
Resources for information on distance learning and for contacting others in the field for assistance. Includes World Wide Web sites, addresses for journals and newsletters, and information on electronic discussion lists.
<P>
<A HREF="#1">Institutional Web Sites</A><BR>
<A HREF="#2">Meta Lists</A><BR>
<A HREF="#3">Electronic Discussion Lists (Listservs)</A><BR>
<A HREF="#4">Journals and Newsletters</A> <BR>
<A HREF="#5">AskERIC Reference Service</A>
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
