<A NAME="3"><STRONG>Electronic Discussion Lists (Listservs)</STRONG></A>
<P>
<STRONG><EM>Distance Education Online Symposium (DEOS-L)</EM></STRONG><BR>
DEOS-L is an international discussion forum for distance learning
sponsored by The American Center for the Study of Distance Education at
Pennsylvania State University. Its purpose is "to promote communication
among distance educators, and to disseminate information and requests
about distance education around the world."<BR>
Subscription information: <A HREF="http://www.cde.psu.edu/ACSDE/DEOS.html">http://www.cde.psu.edu/ACSDE/DEOS.html</A><BR>
Archive of messages: <A HREF="gopher://UKCC.uky.edu:70/1menu%20NETNEWSE%21191/DEOS-L.*">gopher://UKCC.uky.edu:70/1menu%20NETNEWSE%21191/DEOS-L.*</A>
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
<A NAME="4"><STRONG>Journals and Newsletters</STRONG></A>
<P>
