<FONT  SIZE=+1><STRONG>Asymetrix Unveils Neuron&#153: A ToolBook Plug-in for Netscape Navigator</STRONG></FONT>
<P>
<HR>
<P>
<STRONG>The IAT would like to make our friends aware of a new internet tool from Asymetrix:</STRONG>

<UL>

<DL><STRONG>BELLEVUE, WA.</STRONG> - May 7, 1996 - Asymetrix Corporation today announced 
immediate availability of the beta version of the 
<A HREF="http://www.asymetrix.com/toolbook/neuron/index.htm">Neuron&#153; Plug-in</A> 
giving Internet access to all titles produced with any of the Asymetrix 
ToolBook 4.0 line.  Neuron allows end users to download and 
play presentations, kiosks, courseware and other multimedia titles produced 
in ToolBook over the Internet. </DL>
</UL>

<P><STRONG>Note</STRONG>:  The 32-bit <STRONG>beta</STRONG> plug-in is for use with Netscape 2.0 (or higher) running under Windows 95 or Windows NT.
<P>
