<CENTER><STRONG><FONT  SIZE=+2><FONT SIZE=+3>E</FONT>xpress <FONT SIZE=+3>A</FONT>uthor</FONT> </STRONG> </CENTER>
<BR>


<P><center>[<A HREF="#demo">Demo</A> | <A HREF="#prices">Prices</A>] | <A HREF="#order">Order Info</A>] </center>
<HR>
<H3>What is Express Author?</H3>
<P>Express Author allows you to create interactive multimedia applications, prototypes and presentations quickly without programming.  Express Authors intuitive interface makes it an ideal tool for people new to interactive multimedia.  
<P>For those people who need more advanced interactive functions, Express Author applications can  be enhanced with Asymetrix Corporations powerful OpenScript programming language.
<P>Express Author supports digital video, CD-audio, MIDI, digital audio, animation, still images, laserdisc and overlay video.  
<P>Express Author includes:
<UL>
<LI>Online and Printed Tutorials -- Learn how  to use Express Author quickly.
<LI>Clipmakers -- Create, annotate and organize multimedia clips.
<LI>Multimedia Note Fields -- Display text associated with a multimedia clip.
<LI>Clip Databases -- Organize multimedia clips by subject.
<LI>Glossary Tool -- Link definitions and illustrations to hotwords.
<LI>Synchronized Text -- Add captioning to CD-audio and laserdisc playback.
<LI>Sequenced Multimedia Clips -- Play multiple clips from any object without scripting.
<LI>Object Database -- Copy frequently-used multimedia and miscellaneous objects.
</UL>
<HR>
<H3><A NAME="demo">Demonstration</A> Program on the Internet </H3>
<P>There is an Express Author demonstration program available on the Internet (fully functional but does not allow you to save your work).  To access:
<P>If you have <A HREF="../webapp/index.html">WebApp</A> installed on your computer, then you can <A HREF="express.wai">download and install</A> Express Author with a single click of the mouse. DO NOT attempt this before installing WebApp!<BR><B>Warning: This is a 2+ MB file. Make sure you have sufficient room on your target drive.</B>
<P>
<B><A HREF="ftp://ftp.iat.unc.edu/pub/express/demo11a.exe">Via Anonymous FTP</A></B><P>
<HR>
<H3>Customer Support and Information</H3>
<P>Call 919-405-1927 or send an e-mail note to <A HREF="mailto:express_author@unc.edu">express_author@unc.edu</A>
<P><B>Note</B> -- Adding OpenScript commands requires a copy of Asymetrix ToolBook, which is not included with Express Author.<P>
