NOTES: 
<BR>
Web and email addresses in <EM>IAT Infobits</EM> articles are verified at the time of publication. However, some URLs in older issues may have been changed or deleted. When notified, we do update URLs in back issues.
<P>
HTML-versions of 1993 and 1994 issues of <EM>IAT Infobits</EM> may differ from the originally-distributed issues. During the HTML conversions, old URLs were checked and updated to point to the resources' current locations. For copies of issues as they were originally distributed see the archive at URL <A HREF="http://www.iat.unc.edu/infobits/text/index.html">http://www.iat.unc.edu/infobits/text/index.html</A>
