<P><FONT SIZE=+2>About Tom Wason</FONT>
<P><STRONG>Thomas D. Wason</STRONG>, PhD, IAT Special Projects, leads new projects in computer-based training and distributed learning. He is an experimental psychologist with a BS in engineering. Dr. Wason has over 20 years of industry experience including research and development, manufacturing and biomedicine, and has worked in human-computer interaction for over 10 years. He has published papers relating to human perception and has received numerous patents.  

