	Ames, IA: Iowa State Univ. of Science and Technology, Ames
	College of Education. 1992.
<P>
Goldman, Elizabeth. "Using Hypermedia to Improve the Preparation of
	Elementary Teachers." <EM>Journal of Teacher Education</EM> 41 (May-June
	1990): 21-31.
<P>
Griffiths, John, and Ann Degner. "Training for Instructional Uses of
