	Future." <EM>Journal of Educational Technology Systems</EM> 23, no. 4
	(1994-95): 337-353.
<P>
Hannah, C. Lynne, and Ronald J. Abate. "Survey on Faculty Use of
	Interactive Videodisc Technology in Teacher Education." <EM>Journal
	of Educational Technology Systems</EM> 21, no. 4 (1992-93): 321-32.
<P>
Hansford, Brian C. "Evaluation of a Cross-Campus Interactive Video
	Teaching Trial." <EM>Distance Education</EM> 11, no. 2 (1990): 287-307.
<P>
