	Technology in Science Assessment." <EM>Journal of Computers in
	Mathematics and Science Teaching</EM> 12, no. 3/4 (1993): 227-243.
<P>
Herrmann, A., and B. O'Connell. "An Evaluation of Developer and User
	Reactions to Interactive Courseware Based on Repurposed Linear
