	with Media: Restructuring the Debate." <EM>Educational Technology
	Research and Development</EM> 42, no. 2 (1994): 31-39.
<P>
Jones, Loretta L., and Stanley G. Smith. "Can Multimedia Instruction
	Meet Our Expectations?" <EM>EDUCOM Review</EM> 27 (January/February
	1992): 39-43.
<P>
