	Low Socio-Economic Status." <EM>Media and Technology for Human
	Resource Development</EM> 5, no. 3 (1993): 237-242.
<P>
Kaufman, David, and S. Lee. "Formative Evaluation of a Multimedia CAL
	Program in an Ophthalmology Clerkship." <EM>Medical Teacher</EM> 15, no.
	4 (1993): 327-340.
<P>
Kirkwood, Adrian. "Case Study--Bearing Fruit: The Longer-term Effects
