	Training Technology International</EM> 30, no. 4 (1993): 343-53.
<P>
<IMG SRC="../media/gifs/new.gif" BORDER=0 ALT="NEW"> Kitz, William R., and H. W. Thorpe. "A Comparison of the Effectiveness of Videodisc 
