<IMG SRC="../media/gifs/update.gif" BORDER=0 ALT="UPDATED"> Software Publishers Association. SPA Self-Audit Kit. Audit kit for corporations to use on a voluntary basis to examine their software use practices and determine if illegal copies are in use.<BR>
