<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFCE7" TEXT="#00006F">
<CENTER><FONT SIZE=+2><STRONG>Selected Sites in the Sciences</FONT></STRONG>
<P>
Complied by:  Lynn Eades, Education Librarian<BR>
Health Sciences Library, UNC-Chapel Hill
<P>
First distributed at the Spring 1995 Conference of the Librarians' Association of the University of North Carolina at Chapel Hill (March 6, 1995)
<BR>
Revised: October 2, 1996</CENTER>
<P>
This list of selected sites is by no means an attempt to be comprehensive on each subject.  These are sites evaluated and found to be useful for teaching and research. 
<P>
<CENTER>
